  "document_one_liner": "Court of Appeal order with reasons granting the First Applicant permission to appeal only on Ground 1, staying the Part 50 orders as to him, and dismissing the renewed applications and stay requests of the Second and Third Applicants.",
  "document_summary": "This is a complex appellate enforcement order with reasons in which the DIFC Court of Appeal considered renewed applications for permission to appeal and related stay requests arising from Part 50 examination orders made in enforcement proceedings linked to ARB-016-2023. The Court dismissed all proposed grounds advanced by the Second and Third Applicants, but granted the First Applicant permission to appeal on a narrow jurisdictional point concerning the reach of Part 50 to individuals outside the UAE, while otherwise rejecting his case.",
